cdata.name: Buddy
cdata.desc:
Buddy is a decentralized application development automation platform. Their vision is to tokenize the app development automation industry. Buddy provides users with features such as Automation Pipelines (Automate application development and deployment with 70+ ready-to-use steps), Sandboxes β (Full-stack previews & test environments that work as automated instant application previews for every code branch), and Integrations (a pallet of dedicated integrations provides comprehensive support for many stacks).

BUD is an ERC20 utility token that powers the platform, working as the 'gas' that fuels the system.
